Class Cell

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.gc28.model.Cell
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Cell extends Object implements Serializable
this class represents a cell, and is used to store information about the card played, the moment the card was played and the side of the card
